snippet.title: WAVER Launch Stream!
snippet.description:
Join us as we count down to the launch of WAVER: A Typing Adventure. We'll show off a little gameplay, and riff on the development of our first proper release.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1393690/WAVER_A_Typing_Adventure/

This has been an amazing journey for us and we'd love for you to come and join us to celebrate! If you drink, crack out a drink. If you don't drink, pick up drinking. It's the big day. Get ready to W A V E.

Useful links:
TGB Schedule: https://samfundev.github.io/
TGB-Schedule/Our Discord server! -- https://discord.gg/qRMNGGZ
